<section>
<h1>Triple-threat professional designer</h1>

<p> What does it mean to be a “triple threat”?</p>

<p>A <strong>triple threat</strong> is a person who is adept in three different fields of activity.</p>

<p><ul>
<li>In a football game, a football player adept at running, kicking, and passing is a triple threat.</li>
<li>A triple threat in the theater is someone who can sing, dance, and act.</li>
</ul></p>

<p>I have the ability to draw, write, and code HTML/CSS. I&rsquo;m an artist, a writer and a web developer, with the ability to think verbally, to think pictorially, and to think in code. I am a triple-threat professional designer.</p>

<p class="last">Mastering any craft requires focus. Mastering multiple skills requires persistence and dedication, practicing each craft and being strategic with an approach.</p>
</section>

