<h3 >Artist and Graphic Designer</h3>

<p>Making art or graphics is a sport. Practicing visual thinking changes the brain and how one thinks and communicates.</p>

<p>I draw and paint, create art and graphics. I like to work with materials including sumi ink, egg tempera and drawing. I have expert Adobe Photoshop and Adobe Illustrator software skills.</p>

<p>I have an arsenal of techniques and skills. I practice spontaneous and improvisational painting to push boundaries and transcend these techniques. Sometimes great ideas pop out.</p>

<p>I&rsquo;ve learned to recognize strong ideas. Mastery requires research. I look for visual clues, to build a visual vocabulary, think about chemistry, composition, and inventing a theme.</p>

